description: Live above it all in this oversized, elegantly updated 1-bedroom, 1-bath condo perched on a high floor in one of Chicago's most coveted lakefront addresses. Wake up every morning to jaw-dropping, panoramic views of Millennium Park, the skyline, and shimmering Lake Michigan - your personal front-row seat to the best of the city.    This light-filled home features a spacious layout, a sleek newer kitchen with modern cabinetry and appliances, and the luxury of in-unit laundry. Every detail is designed for comfort and style, making it the perfect retreat in the heart of downtown. 155 N Harbor Dr offers unmatched amenities: swim year-round in the indoor pool, stay active in the state-of-the-art gym and Yoga room, unwind in the sauna, or host friends on the outdoor sundeck with grills and sweeping city views. With 24-hour door staff, resident lounges, library, Bockwinkel's grocery store, bike storage, dry cleaners, dedicated laundry room, hobby room, party room, package / mail delivery room and children's play rooms, and more, this building delivers true resort-style living.    Just steps to the lakefront, Maggie Daley and Millennium Parks, Michigan Avenue, and all that downtown Chicago has to offer-this is more than a home, it's a lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to own this rare gem in the sky! PS - Parking is rental, starting from $144 per month. 30 minute free guest parking in garage. Building is Pet Friendly - 25lb limit.
